title: 142: RGIII’s gameplan, NFL Week 14 preview and best bowl games
itunes:title: 142: RGIII’s gameplan, NFL Week 14 preview and best bowl games
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the upcoming slate of Week 14 NFL action. The playoff picture takes shape and RGIII is back to try to get the Browns in the win column for the first time all season. DJ and Bucky also give their take on the best college football bowl games.
